WEBVTT

00:00:01.396 --> 00:00:03.824
I'm often asked,

00:00:03.848 --> 00:00:06.296
"What surprised you about the book?"

00:00:06.320 --> 00:00:08.477
And I say, "That I got to write it."

00:00:08.501 --> 00:00:10.655
I would have never imagined that.

00:00:11.330 --> 00:00:13.880
Not in my wildest dreams did I think --

00:00:13.904 --> 00:00:16.182
I don't even consider
myself to be an author.

00:00:17.289 --> 00:00:19.487
And I'm often asked,

00:00:19.511 --> 00:00:21.976
"Why do you think so many
people have read this?

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.226
This thing's selling still
about a million copies a month."

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.976
And I think it's because
spiritual emptiness